name: Fey_Zara
content:
Fey Zara was a Twi'lek female who was the keeper of a cantina, where she offered people quests for the holotables.
Fey Zara first appeared in the 2015 mobile game Star Wars: Galaxy of Heroes, however she was unnamed until Version Update 5/23/2018 where she gave players quests for the holotables.
